(159, 'Financial Update — Mar 2026 (Audit): - 2025 Revenue: ~$30,000 - Current Monthly Revenue: ~$5,000 - Jan 2026 Cash Balance: $90,000 - Monthly Burn (current): $20,000 - Burn expected to reduce further — targeting near-zero in 2-3 months'),
(160, 'From @Anonymous: Agreed with views below – spoke to her today. Spikey – 0 (just hasn’t operated before and surprising lack of ambition for what she has done so far) EO 5| FMF 5| Thesis 5| Price 8 - Speaks well – has a good consultant background and work - Is going deep on product, consumer insights and brands ? Isn’t aiming for a big outcome ? Wants only patient capital ? Is building a team very luxury – will potentially build a new age Kama with a small TG ? Didn’t hear enough depth on what the market is, what consumers are saying, GTM Next – Pass and track for next [Table] [Table]
Convo 2024-09-17T17:59:00.000+05:30 with @Anonymous and @Anonymous: Rachna Bahadur: - Was at Bain and could only work with companies in small capacities - Looking to move deeper into value chain and couldnt find much - Byjus chased me for 6+ months and made an offer to head the international business that I couldnt refuse - Had an opportunity to co-found 82East - couldnt get over the line on the set-up they were offering (good decision in hindside) -  Was one of the most exciting things I refused from all the offers that were coming to me Building a beauty brand focused on women in menopause and menopause segment. Product - Part of the identification was personal and rest research - Delhi & Bombay pincodes - women aged 40-45 and 50-55 to understand whats changing - We speak to women between these age groups. Its more homogenous across different geos - Care is no longer a luxury. Its customer backw...'),
(161, 'Rm notes — Reflections - FF | Concept | Spiky = 0.5 - should validate from BRCs |: ++ Clarity of thought, good articulation around problem space ++ Hard fought learnings from 1st stint - NOT chasing VC or Twitter hype, wants to validate ++ Taking on hard technical problems e.g. OEMs blocking deep links etc ++ Outside in; has studied other players in the market ++ Self taught software engineer ?? Slightly worried this is a missionary profile and NOT a business builder profile ?? Space has been DOA for a long time
Rm notes: 1. Was thinking about doing Master’s 1. Bain 1. Got back into coding after Bain - YouTube video learnings 1. Browser extension 1. Thoughts on device 1. platform agnostic or OEM agnostic | on device layer 1. Wants to challenge → https://www.opal.so/ 1. Building a second brain → Agent on phone 1. Wants to do a Reddit or offline launch to build convection before going to SPC et
Ref from Aniket (Bain) via Ashwin 2025-09-25T15:15:00.000+05:30: 1. Quirky 1. Thinks differently from others 1. Don’t have solid POV on whether he is great at building or a good product guy 1. Generally positive on him, smart guy
prep notes 2025-09-24T21:57:00.000+05:30: 1. Introduced via AeroDome founders who are from IIT Madras ecosystem 1. About Rohith 1. Prev. company was called Flowstate - https://www.flowstate.cc/ 1. New company 1. My notes
